huyu hapa ni mke wangu,

0:04:40.720,0:04:42.160
huyui ni mimi,

0:04:42.160,0:04:46.160
na watoto wetu wawili wa ajabu.

0:04:46.160,0:04:52.160
Mtoto wangu wa kwanza nimemuita Joshua

0:04:52.160,0:04:55.840
kwa sababu ya yale aliyonifanyia Bwana nilipokuja hapa.

0:04:55.840,0:04:57.720
Jina lake ni Joshua.

0:04:57.720,0:04:59.660
Mzaliwa wa pili ni Eliya.

